Privacy Policy

I built the Dollar Scholar as a free app. It is provided by me at no cost and is intended for use as is. To better protect your privacy, I provide this privacy policy notice.
 
Information Collection and Use
This app is built just for calculation purpose and it doesn’t collect any of the user’s information in any way or format.

Log Data
No data is collected or passed on in case of any error(s).

Cookies
No cookies are collected or stored.

Security
There are no registration or login screens in this app. This app can be used completely offline and it has no method of transmission over the internet, or method of electronic storage. 

Links to Other Sites
There are no links to other websites or online resources.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
I may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

This policy is effective as of 2021-07-12

Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about my Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact me at mappyin@icloud.com.
